UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The artist spent months researching and creating a series of intricate sculptures that reflected the beauty and complexity of nature.  Each sculpture was made with a unique combination of materials, and the artist used a variety of techniques.  In the end, however,  the artist wanted each piece to convey a sense of unity and harmony. Subsequent paragraphs reinforce the same line of reasoning with additional examples, helping readers see how the author connects specific observations to a general claim without overstating certainty.',
